@startuml Simple_High_Level_Steps
title Interactive KPI Bluebook - Simple High-Level Workflow

start

:1) Source Code Repository:
Extracts code & comments;

:2) KPI Extraction Module:
 extracts KPIs;

:3) Literate Programming Engine:
processes docs & tags;

:4) AI-Powered Parsing & Annotation:
 analyzes & categorizes;

:5) Bluebook Generation Engine:
compiles results into a Bluebook;

:6) Interactive Enterprise Bluebook (Web Interface):
presents to developers and business team;

:7) User Feedback:
refine and correct KPI details;

if (New feedback provided?) then (Yes)
  :Save changes to Knowledge Base (KB);
  :Re-run Steps 2–6 for refinement;
else (No)
  note right
    Continue using the current Bluebook
  end note
endif

:8) Update any KPI using your default IDE:
open the exact file and line for quick edits;

stop
@enduml